": "2074115919618478487", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2074115919618478487", "text": "Oil markets have swung from fearing a supply shock to pricing a glut\n\nBut production hasn't surged & demand hasn't collapsed. \n\nA traffic jam is clearing, the risk premium has evaporated & sentiment has flipped. \n\nThat's not the same thing as a new oil reality. \n\n#Oil #OOTT #Brent #Hormuz #EnergyMar", "time": "12:59", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 5494, "likes": 78, "replies": 1, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals", "Geopolitics", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2074133047234941231", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074133047234941231", "text": "Ukrainian drones hit Russia's largest refinery, in one of deepest strikes yet\n#oott https://t.co/KqI83Nc6zB", "time": "14:07", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 6423, "likes": 10, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Russia sanctions", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2074137776690250106", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074137776690250106", "text": "Saudi Aramco official selling prices (OSP) for Arab light in USD/bbl vs the respective benchmarks #oott https://t.co/FjZ3ld6j3L", "time": "14:25", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5581, "likes": 27, "replies": 0, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["OPEC+", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2074142589284958588", "url": "https://x.com/OilandEnergy/status/2074142589284958588", "text": "Up to 75% of pre-war oil flows through the Stra